00:05:18.739 --> 00:05:23.540
to Timothy, my dearly beloved son,

00:05:23.540 --> 00:05:27.920
grace, mercy, and peace

00:05:27.920 --> 00:05:32.920
from God the Father and Christ Jesus, our Lord.

00:05:33.619 --> 00:05:35.220
If you've looked at the back of the bulletin

00:05:35.220 --> 00:05:36.100
