00:11:08.279 --> 00:11:12.119
I believe this morning that when you and when

00:11:12.119 --> 00:11:16.479
I acknowledge God's authority in our lives,

00:11:16.479 --> 00:11:18.959
that it will have a great impact.

00:11:18.959 --> 00:11:22.879
It will change the direction of our lives.

