00:11:25.719 --> 00:11:27.759
I mean, I was just a couple of days

00:11:27.759 --> 00:11:29.519
into my senior year of high school

00:11:29.519 --> 00:11:31.479
when I trusted Christ as my Savior,

00:11:31.479 --> 00:11:34.639
when my life was changed radically

00:11:34.639 --> 00:11:38.479
by the truth of being born again.

00:11:38.479 --> 00:11:40.719
And my pastor at that time, you know,

00:11:40.719 --> 00:11:43.039
as a senior in high school, typically,

00:11:43.039 --> 00:11:44.919
you've already been thinking about what you're

00:11:44.919 --> 00:11:46.639
