00:12:54.199 --> 00:12:57.119
When God opens a door, Paul goes forward.

00:12:57.119 --> 00:12:59.399
When God shuts a door, Paul waits.

00:12:59.399 --> 00:13:03.039
Paul understands God's authority.

00:13:03.039 --> 00:13:07.239
By the way, it is far better for God

00:13:07.239 --> 00:13:08.639
to have the authority in your life

00:13:08.639 --> 00:13:11.479
